@model IEnumerable<StudyShare.ViewModels.UserViewModel>
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using StudyShare.Models
@inject UserManager<AppUser> UserManager
@{ 
    ViewData["Title"] = "Quản trị người dùng";
    var currentUserId = UserManager.GetUserId(User);
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="card-header bg-white py-4 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center border-bottom">
            <h4 class="m-0 fw-bold text-primary"><i class="bi bi-people-fill me-2"></i>Tài khoản hệ thống</h4>
            
            <form asp-action="Index" method="get" class="d-flex w-50">
                <div class="input-group rounded-pill overflow-hidden border">
                    <input type="text" name="searchString" class="form-control border-0 bg-light" 
                           placeholder="Tìm tên hoặc email..." value="@ViewData["CurrentFilter"]" />
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit"><i class="bi bi-search"></i></button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table table-hover align-middle mb-0">
                <thead class="table-light">
                    <tr>
                        <th class="ps-4">Thành viên</th>
                        <th>Quyền hạn</th>
                        <th>Trạng thái</th>
                        <th class="text-end pe-4">Thao tác</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    @foreach (var user in Model) {
                        bool isMe = user.Id == currentUserId;
                        bool isSuperAdmin = user.Role == "SuperAdmin";
                        bool isAdmin = user.Role == "Admin";
                        bool isBanned = user.IsBanned || user.WarningCount >= 3;

                        <tr>
                            <td class="ps-4">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <img src="@(string.IsNullOrEmpty(user.Avatar) ? "/images/default-avatar.png" : user.Avatar)" 
                                         class="rounded-circle me-3 border" width="40" height="40" style="object-fit:cover;">
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="fw-bold text-dark">@user.FullName</div>
                                        <small class="text-muted">@user.Email</small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                @if (isSuperAdmin) {
                                    <span class="badge bg-dark rounded-pill"><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning me-1"></i> Super Admin</span>
                                } else if (isAdmin) {
                                    <span class="badge bg-info-subtle text-info border border-info rounded-pill">Quản trị viên</span>
                                } else {
                                    <span class="badge bg-light text-secondary border rounded-pill">Người dùng</span>
                                }
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                @if (isBanned) {
                                    <span class="badge bg-danger-subtle text-danger rounded-3"><i class="bi bi-lock-fill"></i> Khóa</span>
                                } else {
                                    <span class="badge bg-success-subtle text-success rounded-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> OK</span>
                                }
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-end pe-4">
                                <div class="btn-group gap-1">
                                    @* Logic nút Đổi quyền chỉ dành cho Super Admin *@
                                    @if (User.IsInRole("SuperAdmin") && !isSuperAdmin && !isMe) {
                                        <div class="dropdown">
                                            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary rounded-pill" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                                <i class="bi bi-gear"></i>
                                            </button>
                                            <ul class="dropdown-menu shadow border-0">
                                                @if (!isAdmin) {
                                                    <li><form asp-action="ChangeRole" asp-route-userId="@user.Id" asp-route-role="Admin" method="post"><button class="dropdown-item">Lên Admin</button></form></li>
                                                } else {
                                                    <li><form asp-action="ChangeRole" asp-route-userId="@user.Id" asp-route-role="User" method="post"><button class="dropdown-item text-danger">Hạ xuống User</button></form></li>
                                                }
                                            </ul>
                                        </div>
                                    }

                                    @* Nút Khóa/Mở khóa *@
                                    @if (!isSuperAdmin && !isMe) {
                                        <form asp-action="ToggleBan" asp-route-id="@user.Id" method="post">
                                            <button class="btn btn-sm @(isBanned ? "btn-success" : "btn-outline-danger") rounded-pill">
                                                <i class="bi @(isBanned ? "bi-unlock" : "bi-lock")"></i>
                                            </button>
                                        </form>
                                    }
                                    
                                    <a asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@user.Id" class="btn btn-sm btn-light border rounded-pill">
                                        <i class="bi bi-eye"></i>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    }
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>  